The dataset is constructed from public pull requests of five open-source MPC
frameworks (CrypTen, MP-SPDZ, tf-encrypted, SecretFlow, PySyft). The original
upstream code in each repository is governed by its own (also permissive)
licence; the underlying repositories' licences continue to apply to any
code reproduced verbatim in the `patch` and `test_patch` fields.
